casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Timothy Duncan NAEGELE.
No. D-2888.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 16, 2016.
Timothy Duncan Naegele, of Malibu, California, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
